      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>Chronological summary attributed to <persName ref="PRS4711Giyorgis">Giyorgis Walda ʾAmid</persName>,
               including a brief chronology of biblical kings, probably an extract from the 
               <ref type="work" corresp="PRS4711Giyorgi">Tārika Walda ʾAmid</ref>, followed by an outline of Ethiopian kings.
               It was possibly compiled in <date notBefore="1600" notAfter="1705" cert="low">the 17th or begin of the 18th century</date> by
               an unknown Ethiopian author and later included as an introduction to the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2352ShortC">Short chronicles</ref>.</p>
         </abstract>
